channel.title: Kieran Harrison - Arkitek EP [Deep House, Electronic, Techno)
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/kieranxharrison/sets/arkitek-ep
A 4 song EP I created whilst finishing my degree in Architecture (Hence the name)
Inspired by Artists such as Burial, Bicep and the artists involved at Life After Death, After Life and Innervisions, this EP is experimental and very much a homage to those artists.
Let me know what you think!
